**Asian**

**Soups:**
* Miso soup (Japan)
* Tom yum soup (Thailand)
* Pho (Vietnam)
* Wonton soup (China)
* Ramen (Japan)

**Stews:**
* Japanese curry (Japan)
* Korean stew (gamjatang, kimchi stew)
* Chinese hot pot (China)
* Thai green curry (Thailand)
* Vietnamese bun bo hue (beef noodle soup)

**Hot Drinks:**
* Matcha tea (Japan)
* Jasmine tea (China)
* Genmai tea (Japan)
* Ginger tea (China)
* Chrysanthemum tea (China)

**Soups:**

* Spanish gazpacho
* Turkish lentil soup

**Hot Drinks:**
* Turkish coffee
* Italian cappuccino
* Greek frappe
* Spanish horchata
* Moroccan mint tea
